OL,6,FAlmost one in five households
OL,7,Fstruggled to pay their water bill in
OL,8,Fthe last year, Citizens Advice has
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe advisory service found more than a
OL,12,Ffifth (21%) of those who struggled to
OL,13,Fpay found themselves falling into debt
OL,14,Fwith their supplier.
