OL,6,FThe hike in charges, announced in
OL,7,FJanuary, increased the average
OL,8,Fhousehold water and sewerage bill from
OL,9,Funder #500 to more than #600 a year.
OL,11,FHowever, households have been hit
OL,12,Fparticularly hard since April with an
OL,13,Faverage hike of #86 or 20% front-
OL,14,Floaded into the coming year, with
OL,15,Fsmaller percentage increases in each
OL,16,Fof the next four years.
OL,18,FFactoring in inflation, which is added
OL,19,Fto bills each year, the 2025-26
OL,20,Fincrease in the average bill is #123,
OL,21,For 26%.
