OL,6,FThree quarters (75%) of those cutting
OL,7,Ftheir water use due to difficulties
OL,8,Faffording it were reducing bathing or
OL,9,Fshowering, while 63% were limiting
OL,10,Ftoilet flushes and 77% washed their
OL,11,Fclothes less often.
