OL,6,FIn response to Citizens Advice's
OL,7,Ffindings, CCW chief executive Mike
OL,8,FKeil said: "People should be able to
OL,9,Fuse water without the worry of being
OL,10,Fable to afford their bill, but April's
OL,11,Funprecedented rise in charges has
OL,12,Fcompounded the struggles of millions
OL,13,Fof households.
OL,15,F"More people are turning to us to
OL,16,Fcomplain about not being able to
OL,17,Fafford their bill at a time when over
OL,18,Ftwo in five households have told us
OL,19,Fthey've cut spending on essentials
OL,20,Flike food to make ends meet.
