OL,6,F"Water is an essential ` not a luxury
OL,7,F` but we risk seeing more households
OL,8,Fsinking into hardship, unless we put
OL,9,Fan end to the existing postcode
OL,10,Flottery of water company support
OL,11,Fschemes and replace it with fair and
OL,12,Fconsistent help.
OL,14,F"The case for a single social tariff
